libpoc (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial stable release
  * PoC signaling and voice transport protocol
  * Speex audio codec support
  * MS-framed TCP signaling and UDP voice transport
  * Server-side state machine (poc_server_t)
  * Message delivery ACK/NACK and offline notification
  * FEC for voice frame recovery
  * GPS position encoding/decoding
  * AES encryption support
  * 104 tests

